item.dc:creator: @D_D_3 D D 3
item.description:
@D_D_3 wrote:

[quote=“Prozon, post:27, topic:182726”]To Original Poster:
There are none that are really close to Runescape. Everybody adds stupid things in to their private servers or has commands to get free items. I suppose if you have some grudge on Jagex or just want an easier game you could browse the adverts for a popular one. Can’t really promise its going to be like the original Runescape though, or that it will be as glitch-free or maintained as the original.

To El Lama:

this has got to be the stupidest thread ive seen, warn the faggots who spammed this thread up, the original poster was askin wich server u think is closest to rl rs

Posting that was spam aswell. It did not answer the question nor contribute to the thread at all.

To Everyone Else:
If you do not have anything to say referring to the poster’s question, do not post it.[/quote]I bet it took you 20 minutes to type that.The closest server to runescape right now is soulscape made by Sigex or littleplop (same thing).He has req trade starting to get worked on , dodian isn’t the closest it just has stability.
